author: @k-fanatic
text:
Chan,

I want you to know STAY loves you so so much. We are so glad you took this path and is here for us even in our lowest. But Iâ€™m so sorry some of us canâ€™t be here in YOUR lowest. Iâ€™m pretty sure all of us know at this point that youâ€™re struggling with yourself. Please never listen to the haters trying to bring you down, theyâ€™re always trying to make someone feel bad for their benefit. Itâ€™s seriously not fair. Chan, you have no idea how much I and STAYS love you, all around the world. Weâ€™ll support you always, no matter what you do. But please, please never take any hate comments to heart because none of them are true. Youâ€™re so amazing, you have incredible visuals, perfect proportions, a beautiful dance style, an absolutely CHARMING voice, and a smile that could seriously light up somewhere dark. STAYS love seeing your smile, so smile when you mean it. Smile when you feel like it. Iâ€™m serious when I say you have actually saved peoples lives. Iâ€™ve heard of peoples stories, they wanted to die, but they found you, they found Stray Kids, and that saved them. Everyone is so thankful for you and all the members, for being there for us. But Chan, I know youâ€™re struggling more than anyone out there. You have to deal with all this hate and also dealing with yourself, trying to figure out a nice way to respond, in a way you wonâ€™t get even more hate. But ignore them. They only want to see you down, they only want to see you fail. Why are they watching your lives anyway? They want to be seen. They want to be noticed. Even if it means by doing something as horrible as hating on someone that deserves all the love in the world like you. Iâ€™m so so thankful to you, Lee Know, Changbin, Hyunjin, Han, Felix, Seungmin, and I.N. All of you helped me so much and I wouldnâ€™t be as happy as I am now without you guys. I doubt they will ever see this but I hope other STAYS can help me out by spreading this message so that eventually they will be able to see it. Thank you so much Stray Kids. 

Love, STAY â¤â¤

text:
That is so beautiful, sounds almost ethereal, and the lyrics are amazing as always, like, seriously at this point I am more than amazed by the talent Stray Kids possess and the amount of hard work they put into each song they release.
And, of course, Bang Chan's and I.N's vocals are just out of this world!
Thank you very much for this song, it's like a present for the New Year's Eve, so calm and heartwarming, it's like all the stress, I've accumulated in my heart during this year, just disappeared.
I hope Stray Kids will have an amazing year 2024 and I wish you guys to be happy and healthy.
Stray Kids everywhere all around the world!
Stray Kids and Stay together forever!

text:
In the dark night sky
I feel the empty space
The deep chasm between the two stars 
that I found at last disappears

After everything crumbles down, another world is born
Shining brightly in front of my eyes
A whirlwind of time and space, the falling sky
Warmly surrounds and caresses me 

I fall into you again
Into your heart
Leaving myself to gravity
I'm trapped in your space again
There's nothing I can do 

The moment we touch each other amid the stardust
I know that baby you are the one
You and I, our hearts like the stars
Shine brightly for each other

The space that tears apart the night sky
We can't stop
You are my fate,I am your mate
Swirling up the vast emptiness
We will shine

Far away in the distance
You're shining in your place
I am drawn to you
And the blank space in that place

Is it a coincidence or is it meant to be
With you I step into this new world
As the two of us scatter apart
We are surrounded by even more brightness

I fall into you again
Into your heart
The way gravity leads me
I'm trapped in your space
And there's nothing I can do

The moment we touch each other amid the stardust
I know that baby you are the one
You and I, our hearts like the stars
Shine brightly for each other

The space that tears apart the night sky
We can't stop
You are my fate, i am your mate
